            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02304.001.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place">c/o <handShift rend="printed"/>C. V. SKOKOWSKI,<ptr
                            target="loc.02304_n1"/><lb/>36 BROMFIELD STREET,<lb/>BOSTON.</name>
                    <date when="1888-07-24" rend="right"><handShift rend="manuscript"/>24 / July
                        88.</date>
                </dateline>
                <salute>Dear Mr. Whitman,</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>a few days ago I have returned from a short trip to Holland and England. Met
                    Rossetti,<ptr target="n0522"/> young Gilchrist<ptr target="n0262"/> and others
                of your London friends, they all send their love to you. How is your health?</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>Always Yours</salute>
                <signed rend="right">C. Sadakichi Hartmann</signed>
            </closer>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02304.002.jpg"/>
